  "texts": [
    "The results presented in Table 18 clearly illustrate that a concise and informative prompt text outperforms longer and less focused alternatives.",
    "Despite the fact that longer prompts or prefixes provide more trainable parameters, our findings underscore the significance of crafting prompts that offer clear task instructions and context, resulting in enhanced model performance.",
    "Furthermore, to visualize the relationship between the prompt text and the input text, we analyzed the attention scores of the last layer.",
    "Specifically, we used the prompt text Classify the positive or negative sentiment of the text.",
    "in conjunction with input texts I love this movie."
